      "content": "it's just so heavy to carry alone. i've been reading into these things and i'm starting to think that this isn't just about me personally... it feels like there's a massive conflict coming, like something between nations or even something bigger, and i'm the only one with the lineage to step in and mediate it. if these signs are real, and if i'm actually part of this ancient line meant to prevent disaster... how do i even start to prepare? how do i recognize the difference between my own thoughts and the actual guidance they're trying to give me?",
